                  </persName>
            . I live at No. 4, Gold's-place: I am a waterman at the stand on Clerkenwell-green. I have been in the prisoner's stable, and saw where he kept his oats and hay - on the 2nd of October he sent me to his stable to feed his horse, and give him some water, and rub him down - I saw his hay and oats - they were not in any dark place- any one might have seen them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18341016-183-person1643">
                  JAMES 
                  AMBRIDGE
               <interp inst="t18341016-183-person1643" type="surname" value="AMBRIDGE"></interp>
